  In the legend, the data has \'93stat+syst\'94 but in the caption it says just \'93statistical\'94; correct one or the other.\
\cf2 The errors bar in the MC are statistical and also from the cross-talk. However, the uncertainty from the cross-talk is very minimal. The error bars in the tails of the MC are mostly from statistical uncertainty.\
Corrected the plot.\
